criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  moderate to severe COPD (GOLD 2017);

          -  long-term users of nocturnal non-invasive ventilation for chronic hypercapnic
             respiratory failure;

          -  presence of tidal expiratory flow limitation in the supine position at an expiratory
             positive airway pressure of 4 cmH2O.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  COPD exacerbation within the past two months;

          -  acute illness;

          -  clinical instability.
